	<h2>Web Application</h2>
	<p>This web application is to help you setup your UDRC with a Gateway.  You will need to <a href='/login'>login</a> 
		in order to edit operating parameters.  Required parameters will be highlighted <input required value='like this'
	/>.
	</p>
